{
  "stem": "23579.6",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "After four hours, I saw my brother, the oldest-- Motele, came in.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And waving to me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I said, OK, I see my brother.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And when he came on the-- on, yeah, they let him in on the-- on the ship, I said, tell me only the truth.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I don't want to-- I don't want to go down.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I have such a bad feelings, I said.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Tell me, what is with Itzchak-- I mean Zalman.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "He said yes, mein kind, I didn't-- I couldn't-- I couldn't come.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I was four hours waiting till I-- I was OK to come to you.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No-- I came straight--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Israel, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he knew, because the people that-- from the Israeli [NON-ENGLISH], they told him that we are coming.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You understand?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They told him.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he was a very big shishke.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He was, too, a Palmachnik.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He was working.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He was a captain in the Palmach.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He was always working for the [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he said this is it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I said, tell me, how has it happened?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What is it happened?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he told me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "This is the story.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "This is.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And down from the ship, we went right away to Tel Aviv.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "From Tel Aviv, we went to Kibbutz Dan.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was in Kibbutz Dan.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Lilke went, Tuvia and me and Zus.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were in Kibbutz Dan about four days.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the Syrian began their to shooting.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "This was terrible, and I was-- I was all shaking up.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "As Zus said, I'm sorry, I cannot stay with her here.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I have to take her to Tel Aviv, because she will fail-- she will be sick.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And that's what happened.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We went right away to Tel Aviv.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And there was one working [NON-ENGLISH] in the Szochnut, Cohen, in the Szochnut.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Cohen.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Cohen.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
